================================================================================
LOOP FLOW CONTRIBUTION ANALYSIS
================================================================================

  Baseline FBMC Savings:        6,357,506 EUR (12.63%)
  Isolated FBMC Savings:        4,309,107 EUR (10.70%)
  --------------------------------------------------
  Loop Flow Contribution:       2,048,398 EUR (32.2% of baseline savings)
  Remaining FBMC Benefit:       4,309,107 EUR (67.8% of baseline savings)

================================================================================
HYPOTHESIS EVALUATION
================================================================================

  HYPOTHESIS: FBMC benefits arise primarily from loop flows
              through Norwegian interconnections.

  EVIDENCE:
    - Loop flow contribution: 32.2% of total FBMC savings
    - Savings reduction when NO connections removed: 1.93pp

  VERDICT: SUPPORTED
  Loop flows account for significant portion of FBMC benefits

